-- frame 9: trace-A (soft cell, LLM evaluation вҖ” full execution trace)
-- в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ

вҠў trace-A
  given program-AвҶ’execution-order-A вүЎ ["input-data", "weighted-sum-A", "total-weight-A", "weighted-average-A"]
  given input-dataвҶ’values вүЎ [10, 20, 30, 40]
  given input-dataвҶ’weights вүЎ [1, 2, 3, 4]
  yield frames-A[], final-state-A

  вҲҙ Execute program A step by step following В«program-AвҶ’execution-order-AВ».
    For each step, record:
    - Which cell was evaluated
    - What its inputs resolved to
    - What its yields were bound to
    - Which oracle checks passed

    Frame format per step:
    { step: N, cell: "name", inputs: {...}, yields: {...}, oracles: [pass/fail] }

    After all steps, record the final-state-A as the complete set of
    frozen yield bindings across all cells.

-- LLM evaluation:
-- The LLM follows the execution-order-A and simulates eval-one for each cell.
-- It has access to the cell definitions via the program graph and the concrete
-- input values. It traces through each step deterministically.

  yield frames-A вүЎ [
    { step: 0, cell: "input-data", inputs: { values: [10,20,30,40], weights: [1,2,3,4] }, yields: { values: [10,20,30,40], weights: [1,2,3,4] }, oracles: ["len=len вң“", "len>=1 вң“", "all positive вң“"] },
    { step: 1, cell: "weighted-sum-A", inputs: { values: [10,20,30,40], weights: [1,2,3,4] }, yields: { weighted-sum: 300 }, oracles: ["300=300 вң“"] },
    { step: 2, cell: "total-weight-A", inputs: { weights: [1,2,3,4] }, yields: { total-weight: 10 }, oracles: ["10=10 вң“"] },
    { step: 3, cell: "weighted-average-A", inputs: { weighted-sum: 300, total-weight: 10 }, yields: { average: 30 }, oracles: ["30=30 вң“"] }
  ]
  yield final-state-A вүЎ {
    input-dataвҶ’values: [10,20,30,40],
    input-dataвҶ’weights: [1,2,3,4],
    weighted-sum-AвҶ’weighted-sum: 300,
    total-weight-AвҶ’total-weight: 10,
    weighted-average-AвҶ’average: 30
  }

